<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199153>
    bibo:endPage "16" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "2671" ;
    dc:creator "Rojas-Runjaic, Fernando J. M.; Infante-Rivero, Edwin E.; Cabello, Pedro; Velozo, Pablo" ;
    dc:date "2010" ;
    dc:title "A new non-sexually dichromatic species of the genus Gonatodes (Sauria: Sphaerodactylidae) from Sierra de Perijá, Venezuela" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199154>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199155>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199156>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199157>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199158>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199159>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199160> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199154>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Gonatodes lichenosus sp. nov.: a. Male holotype (MHNLS 19116); b. Female paratype (MHNLS 19107)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/199154/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199155>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Details of dorsal (a), lateral (b), and ventral (c) views of the head of Gonatodes lichenosus sp. nov. (male holotype, MHNLS 19116). Scale bar represents 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/199155/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199156>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Dorsal view of Gonatodes lichenosus sp. nov. (male holotype MHNLS 19116), showing clusters of enlarged, conical to spinelike scales on the flanks of neck and trunk. White arrows indicate the clusters of scales magnified in upper right and lower left frames." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/199156/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199157>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Gonatodes lichenosus sp. nov. (male holotype, MHNLS 19116): a. Ventral view showing escutcheon areas on posterior part of belly and undersurface of thighs; b. Detail of subcaudal scale pattern; c. Ventral view of left hand (scale bar represent 1 mm); d. Ventral view of left foot (scale bar represents 2 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/199157/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199158>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Variation on dorsal (a) and ventral (b) color pattern of the type series of Gonatodes lichenosus sp. nov.; a: from left to right, female paratypes MHNLS 19107 and 19111, and male paratypes MHNLS 19109 and 19110; b: from left to right, female paratypes MHNLS 19107 and 19111, and male paratypes MHNLS 19110 and 19109. Note the absence of sexual dichromatism in both views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/199158/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199159>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Map of NW Venezuela showing major physiographic elements: Maracaibo Lake, and Sierra de Perijá to the west. Type locality of Gonatodes lichenosus sp. nov. is shown by a white circle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/199159/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199160>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. a: General view of the Manastara valley in the Sierra de Perijá, estado Zulia, Venezuela, area where Gonatodes lichenosus sp. nov. inhabits; b – c: views of the Manastara community and the microhabitat where five specimens of the type series were collected." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/199160/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

